<section>
  <title><xref ref="S_otherinduction"></xref></title>
  <subsection>
    <title><xref ref="prog_extendedind"></xref></title>
    <ol>
      <li>
        <p>
          For each natural number <m>n</m>,
          if <m>n \geq 2</m>, then <m>3^n > 1 + 2^n</m>.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p>
          For each natural number <m>n</m>,
          if <m>n \geq 6</m>, then <m>2^n > (n + 1 )^2</m>.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p>
          For each natural number <m>n</m>, if <m>n \geq 6</m>,
          then <m>\left( 1 + \dfrac{1}{n} \right)^n > 2.5</m>.
        </p>
      </li>
    </ol>
  </subsection>
